        <span>Hi @Model.FirstName,</span>

        <h1 style="text-align: center;">wishlu is the new way to give (and to get).</h1>
        <h2 style="text-align: center;">Here's a few ideas of what to ask for...</h2>

        @if (Model.Gender == 'f')
        {
            <h3>To get creative.</h3>
            <p>
                Love photography? Adore painting? There's a wishlu waiting to be made for every palette of passionate pursuits.
            </p>

            <div style="text-align:center;">
