            <p>
                Polished skills never go out of style. Exploring your most cerebral curiosities with a highly intelligent wishlu: language courses, titles on required reading lists, and night classes to light up your entrepreneurial IQ.
            </p>

            <div style="text-align:center;">
                <img style="width:100%;" src="http://assets.wishlu.com/images/tutorial/wishlus/bookshelf.png" />
            </div>
            <br />
            @Button("http://www.wishlu.com/wishlu", "create a wishlu now")
            
            <h3>To get gorgeous.</h3>
            <p>
                Something on everyone's wish list: a well-stocked make-up bag. Create a wishlu that lets loved ones makeover yours with new finds, luxe beauty loot, and all of your tried-and-true staples.
            </p>

