            </div>
            <br />
            @Button("http://www.wishlu.com/wishlu", "create a wishlu now")            
        }
        else
        {
            <h3>To get going.</h3>
            <p>
                Not having the right tools can stand in the way of your very best intentions. Make a wishlu to ask for what you need, please, and tackle that to-do list and DIY projects.
            </p>
    <!-- Illustration of wishlus with items specified -->
            <br />
            @Button("http://www.wishlu.com/item/hunt", "search for tools now")
            
            <h3>To get growing.</h3>
            <p>
                From seeds to sprouts, from roots to blooms, a well-tended-to wishlu helps unearth your latent green thumb.
            </p>

            <div style="text-align:center;">
                <img style="width:100%;" src="http://assets.wishlu.com/images/tutorial/wishlus/my%20garden.png" />
            </div>
            <br />
            @Button("http://www.wishlu.com/wishlu", "create a wishlu now")
            

