            <p>
                Feed your need for gizmos. An updateable wishlu keeps you current, connected, and on the cutting edge with the latest and greatest tech-savvy gear.
            </p>

            <div style="text-align:center;">
                <img style="width:100%;" src="http://assets.wishlu.com/images/tutorial/wishlus/gadgets.png" />
            </div>
            <br />
            @Button("http://www.wishlu.com/item/hunt", "search for gadgets now")
            
